{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Combine the digital tachograph with the driver CPC (DQC) card",
        "additional_details": "Having trained hundreds of drivers and spoken to hundreds of transport managers everyone agrees there should be an alignment of both cards you need both to work and a simple alignment so you cannot get a digital card without completing 35h training",
        "background": "Currently you need a 5yr digital tachograph card to record your actions and the driver CPC card to prove you have completed 35h training over 5 years if you don't have your CPC card you will be fined \u00a350.00 if you are driving commercial vehicles you need to have both with you a legal requirement",
